	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think i remotely read somewhere that the snes and the n64 cic's share some similarities. Is there a possibilty that with the knowledge that now is known from the super nintendo cic's and n64 cic's, that a n64 chip could be made? I would love a region free n64 with 50/60hz feature as the superCIC for the N64? I guess it's a lot of hard work and tinkering, but I just figured that I could ask at least, if anybody is working on it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


